HEADWORD: Zoochlorella
<hw>Zo`o*chlo*rel"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
dim. from Gr. <grk>zw^,on</grk> an animal + <?/ green.]</ety>
